text: The Cycle (, Dayereh-ye Mina, also Romanized as Dāyere-ye Minā) is a 1975 Iranian drama movie directed by Dariush Mehrjui. It stars Saeed Kangarani, Ezzatolah Entezami, Forouzan, Ali Nassirian. ==Other websites== * Category:1975 drama movies Category:Iranian movies Category:Movies directed by Dariush Mehrjui
title: The Cycle (1975 movie)
